review_blob: Gives you almost a sweet caramel taste going down and then all the flavors kick in at once. You get the fruit taste and then a strong kick at the end of the pallets. Great beer I would recommend to a lot of friends.
beer_name: Widmer Brothers / Cigar City Gentlemens Club - Rye Whiskey Barrel

review_blob: Went to the new local brewery in Livermore. I do have to say most of there selections are very tasty. This double IPA was fantastically smooth and less bitter compared to there shelter IPA. The smell was nice and fruity. Top layer tasted nice. These guys are definitely headed I the right direction. When I was in there I saw the owner trying what looked to be a new beer and It looked like a Hef so this should be exciting.

beer_brewer_name: Schneider Weisse G. Schneider & Sohn GmbH
review_blob: This was a fantastic beer right down to the bottle. It smelt great and wend down very smooth. As I was at the pub I was on y phone looking to see if the local bevmo had it. I recommend this to all beer drinkers!!
